verbose_text: The mRNA expression of IL-17 in PDN group (0.85 +/- 0.12) was significantly lower than that in control group (1.25 +/- 0.10) (p < 0.01, Figure XREF_FIG a) and the mRNA expression of IL-17 in PDN + CTK group (1.04 +/- 0.07) was significantly lower than that in CTK group (2.00 +/- 0.17) (p < 0.01, Figure XREF_FIG a).
